text: Tsubasa Sasaki (born 23 March 1995) is a Japanese slalom canoeist who has competed at the international since 2010. He finished 12th in the C2 event at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro together with Shota Sasaki. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male canoeists Category:Olympic canoeists of Japan Category:Canoeists at the 2016 Summer Olympics
